#Code written by:
#Name: 				Shreya Gupta


	Image manipulation codes:


-Geometric Wapring
-Panoramic Stitching
-Digital Halftoning: fixed thresholding, random thresholding and Dithering
-Morphological image processing: Shrinking, thinning, skeletonizing, counting stars
-Texture Classification
-RGB to grayscale conversion
-Image resizing using bilinear interpolation
-Histogram equalization
-Oil painting effect
-Image denosing 
-Texture Segmentation



Installation:
Unzip source code zip file at a convinient location.
make clean && make

Testing:
cd bin/
1. For Geometric Warping
	Usage  : ./geometericWarping <input image> <width> <height> <bits per pixel>
	Example: ./geometericWarping panda.raw 512 512 3


2. For Panoramic Stitching
	Usage  : ./panoramicStitching <input image1> <width> <height> <bits per pixel> <input image 2><input image 3>
	Example: ./panoramicStitching middle.raw 480 640 3 left.raw right.raw


3. For Digital Halftoning
	Usage  : ./digitalHalftoning <input image> <input_width> <input_height> <input bits per pixel> <type of thresholding>
	(type=1:Fixed )
	(type=2:Random)
	(type=3:Dithering using Bayer's matrix)
	Example: ./digitalHalftoning colorechecker.raw 512 512 1 1


4. For Morphological Image processing operation
	Usage  : ./morphology <input image>  <input_width> <input_height> <input bits per pixel> 
	Example: ./morphology star.raw 640 480 1

5. For Texture Classification
	Usage  : ./texture_classification 
	Example: ./texture_classification 

6. For RGB to Grayscale
	Usage  : ./rgb2gray <input image> <width> <height> <bits per pixel>
	Example: ./rgb2gray Tiffany.raw 512 512 3

7.  For Image Resizing
	Usage  : ./imageResizing <input image> <input_width> <input_height> <input bits per pixel> <output_width> <output_height>
	Example: ./imageResizing Airplane.raw 512 512 3 650 650

8. For Histogram Equalization
	Usage  : ./histogramEqualization <input image> <input_width> <input_height> <input bits per pixel> 
		       
	Example: ./histogramEqualization Desk.raw 400 300 3 
	         ./Bucket Desk.raw 400 300 3

9. For Oil Painting Effect
	Usage  : ./oilPaintingEffect <input image> <width> <height> <bits per pixel> <window size> <colors> 
	Example: ./oilPaintingEffect Barn.raw 380 275 3 5 64

10.For Denoising
	Usage  : ./denoising <input image>  <input_width> <input_height> <input bits per pixel> <window size> <original_image>
	Example: ./denoising Lena_mixed.raw Lena.raw 512 512 3 5 Lena.raw

11. For Texture Segmentation
	
	Usage  : ./textureSegmentation <input image>  <input_width> <input_height> <input bits per pixel> 
	Example: ./textureSegmentation comb.raw 600 450 1


	
	


